# EVENT::SUPPRESS_SHOCKING_EVENT_TYPE_NEXT_FRAME

## Summary
Prevents shocking events of a certain type from being added to the world next frame

## Parameters
* **SHOCKING_EVENT_LEVEL** eventShockingLevel
